These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-1::.
7 different games are played: canasta, backgammon, mah-jongg, poker, bridge, whist, snooker
1. the person playing backgammon is in the middle##1
2. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
3. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person playing poker##1
4. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
5. the person playing snooker is on the far left##1
6. the person playing whist is on the right of the person playing canasta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |    4     |   5    |   6   |    7     |
| Game   | snooker | poker | bridge | backgammon | mah-jongg | canasta | whist |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-2::.
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: basketball, weightlifting, snowboarding, baseball, cycling, handball, sailing
1. the person who's sport is sailing is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far left##1
3. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
4. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
5. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
6. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |    2    |      3       |   4   |     5     |   6    |    7    |
| Sport   | basketball | cycling | snowboarding | handball | baseball | weightlifting | sailing |

