1. the gothic-revival house is on the far left##1
2. the modern house is on the left of the townhouse house##1
3. the ranch-style house is on the far right##1
4. the palace house is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
5. the cape-cod house is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3      |    4    |    5     |    6    |    7    |
| House   | gothic-revival | modern | townhouse | cape-cod | wooden | palace | ranch-style |

