.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-5::.
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: august, february, december, june, april, october, january
1. the person who's birthday is in october is in the middle##1
2. the person who's birthday is in january is on the far left##1
3. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
4. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
5. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
6. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |    2     |   3    |   4   |    5     |     6      |   7   |
| Birthday   | january | december | june | october | august | february | april |

