2. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
3. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
4. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
5. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |    4    |    5    |    6    |    7    |
| Birthday   | october | november | february | september | january | december | may |

 